# Loaded for `vite build` / production. Overrides: `.env.production.local` (gitignored).
# Path `/v1` = same origin as the deployed SPA; nginx (or your host) proxies `/v1` to the backend—client does not need the backend port.
# Only set an absolute URL if the browser must talk to a different host/port than the page (cross-origin API).
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/v1
# Optional: set `VITE_S3_PUBLIC_BASE_URL` + `VITE_S3_BUCKET` to match messaging-service (`S3_PUBLIC_BASE_URL` + `S3_BUCKET`) for thread image URLs.
